description: Team marinated chicken drumsticks with corn cobs and potato wedges for a simple midweek meal where the oven does most of the work for you.
keywords: Smoky Barbecue Chicken & Corn Tray Bake
name: Smoky Barbecue Chicken & Corn Tray Bake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1.4 kg Woolworths RSPCA approved chicken drumsticks

recipeInstructions.text: Arrange chicken, potatoes and corn on a large baking tray. Drizzle with oil and bake for 40 minutes, adding onion halfway through cooking, or until chicken is cooked and potatoes are golden. Serve topped with coriander.
